NIST PIV Test Data Software - Modernized

This package contains the original NIST PIV Test Data Software (version 1.0.3, July 2007) 
with modern wrapper scripts to facilitate cross-platform usage.

ORIGINAL NIST SOFTWARE:
The original PIV Test Data Software was developed by the National Institute of Standards 
and Technology (NIST) and is in the public domain. NIST assumes no responsibility 
whatsoever for the use of this software by other parties.

MODERNIZATION ENHANCEMENTS:
The modernization wrapper scripts and build system are provided as-is for educational 
and research purposes. These enhancements facilitate the use of the original NIST 
software on modern systems.

DISCLAIMER:
This software is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. The authors and 
contributors are not responsible for any damages or issues that may arise from 
the use of this software.

SECURITY NOTICE:
This software is intended for testing and development purposes only. Do not use 
in production environments without proper security review.